\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you make music as a family, did you all sing together as a family?
