\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. We did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Tell me about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well - there was a - well I - I can't tell you of it - it come out - come about. They were much out of work with it, 
you couldn't get a job then when you come out of work could you. Not my days. I don't think you could. If a man were out of work - well, he had nothing - had he. You see, we'd nothing, we never paid to anything. You couldn't save - you couldn't save for n
o
thing because you had nothing. Working people couldn't save for anything. You never went - here, you hear them tell where they're going, they're flying now, they couldn't afford to go on a - for a holiday, proper holiday. They were - we used to think, eeh
 aren't we well off going away for a day or two, no weeks then you know allowed. Oh we'd see send away a family, just for a day or two, that was their holiday, you - you used to thing they were well off. You weren't. Anyway we didn't bother.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You knew a lot of well off people did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well not really, just like as ourselves you know. If they had they went, if they didn't they'd have to stop home, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What class do you think you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh working class, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you remember someone being referred to as a real lady and why do you think it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Eeh I don't know - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What about a gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh we used see some nice gentleman in town. We - you know, we used think, they're well off. Would walk -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
I don't know, we used to think because they were dressed nice, really nice you know. Like they used to do but - there's nobody dresses nice now if you ask me out. I don't think there's anything nice about how they dress now. Well I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You like the minis you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 I'd rather have short skirts than long skirts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Why didn't you like long skirts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well I didn't like long skirts. Well you could get about better in - I think - with these }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9313129\charrsid3816264 shorter}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  skirts on. I found - found it out since I had mine a little shorter. You can get there better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You mean when you were working long skirts were a nuisance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh they were a nuisance, yes, even the mill skirts were - we used to wear skirts to work in - washing - what wash you k
now. Oh yes. We didn't wear - we used to take our dress skirt off and - we used to have a - a blouse on what was made for work and we used to put another skirt, a working skirt, what we - oh yes, they use - they were stripe - happen about this and then yo
u know -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 A special striped skirt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. To work in, working skirts. Oh yes. And me - me grandma used to make then us. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When you were a child were you ever taught to curtsey to anyone or call someone sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh well we knew th
at. Well we knew with the looks of people. Well we could call anybody sir couldn't you. Why not? There's - they're as fit be called sir as anybody else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Who would you call sir as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well I call - well the schoolmaster and - people like that you know, what we thought were a little - higher than us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Who were the most important people that you remember as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 We'd - higher than us like? Well, we used to think the schoolmaster, the school teachers and when we went to Sunday scho
ol and the priest or minister or what he might be and there were doctors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 They were important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Oh very important. And were they good. Oh I think they were. What did they used to get. They were satisfied with threepence. That's Monday morning. No
w grandma's given our doctors bill threepence or sixpence at Monday morning many a time. Were they ever paid? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 The doctors weren't paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 The doctors were never paid, they - doctors is all - they're owing pounds and pounds I'm sure to doctors. What they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Who do you think the shopkeepers mixed with where you lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Oh they were all right. They used to go - anybody as they let have something on - 'til weekend and they used to go and pay them, well them as didn't pay them and they k
new some were awkward couldn't get their money, well they used to help to put them in court or something like that to get their money, you know, they had to do it so - don't pay you know. Well why did they get when they know they can't afford to pay.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Who did the teachers mix with do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 I don't know I'm sure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Who do you think the employers mixed with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well I think they mixed up with the class of - their own class of people same as working people did. They always mixed - yes, th
ey mixed with their own people. Well I think they did. We always were with our own kind of people. They were all right. We were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Can you tell me if there was a difference between the people that went to church when you were a girl and the people who went to chapel?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Who went to where? Well they didn't go to church like we went. Church people, they used send their children to Sunday school at th'afternoon. They never went to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You're thinking the Catholics went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well - you never saw 'em going, they - they'd like a bed some of them of a Sunday morning. We were never allowed to lie in bed. Never.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you know any chapel people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well they weren't so many went chapel. The chapellers, no. My husbands been s
topped many a time, he said to my husband, hey I wish t'ours 'd turn up like your lot does. Our church - church opens four times and there's always plenty in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When you were a girl did you notice any difference socially between people who went to chapel and the people who went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Oh I don't know luv. Oh I don't think as they were any worse off with us, you know, nasty with us or anything, oh no, oh no, we weren't - nothing do with us. We had to go, we knew we had to go and we went, we neve
r bothered. But we used go every Sunday morning. And many a time at night we had to go and at Sunday school at two o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever feel when you were a girl that some people thought they were better than others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh yes, they'd come and think they were, but they weren't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Why?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9313129\charrsid3816264 
Well I don't know, they happen got a few shillings more than our father's got, you know, sometime they do it like that, they say, well her father works - he's a spinner, he has wheels. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Got }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9313129\charrsid3816264 wheels}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 He's a craftsman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, like they would say a craft. Well they didn't get all that much. If he got thirty shilling I think that were a good wage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 So you thought there was a difference between craftsman and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What about the labourers, would they be very poor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Oh well, they only got eighteen shillings you know. Some didn't get - some got eighteen shillings and they used to have to pay tuppence union out of that luv. What had they to take home to their wives. Now some - some were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  and they were - the side piece - only were side piecing, they only got fourteen and sixpence a week and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
. And plenty, not one - or two - plenty was like that. Because my brother were one as were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  getting fourteen and si
xpence, him as I told you got me dad's wheels. But his wife went working. They had a baby and it died so she went working after it died. Of course she'd more after, of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When you were a child do you think people could move up in the worked, did 
you ever know anybody who moved up in the world and how do you think they did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well no, I don't know, I don't know. I don't know luv.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you ever remember anybody going down in the world?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well - well I don't know, I couldn't say that ei
ther. I couldn't. Don't know as I know anybody going up or coming down luv, not as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You thought of some people as rough and some as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh yes, oh yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Tell me the difference between the two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 And - and still when they were with you they were no different }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9313129\charrsid3816264 to us}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 , you get me, but we knew which were which you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 How?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9313129\charrsid3816264 Well - they had a rough way kind of thing, wasn't nice with you kind but then they'd come and want to be - fuss about you, you know 
'til you got with them again. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Or else - otherwise I don't think we were bad. No, I don't really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You don't think there was a lot of difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. No, not there. They'd no need to be, one had no more than the other as I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you rem
ember seeing a policeman round your house, did - your grandmother used to frighten you if you did anything wrong did she ever say I'll tell a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, not as I know of. Not to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you remember the police round your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh yes, they used to come round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Were they good, how did they treat the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Oh they were all right, they - oh talk to you if you were passing. Like just say good morning, that's all. They used to have their beat, you know, on the beat, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 They treated you all right though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh yes, policemen were all right. To my knowledge you know. Yes, I've never known nothing - about the policeman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Was your house rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever see the landlord and what did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 He - he - see - I'd see landlord coming for - I don't know how much they were a week, they wasn't so dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What did you think of the landlord, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh he used to be all right, was always dressed nice, you know, when they come for your rent, yes, always dressed nice, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you feel that your father and granny had a struggle to make ends meet and how did you feel about it as a child?
\par 
