soft ball and we used play catchers, stand round you know, we'd play catch-it. Anybody could join in as were on the sands, join in with us, the boys you know what with our girl, used say, come on, you can have a catch it round. Same with cricket - go and 
run after ball and then you can bat when It's your turn, we used do that when we were on. Well they were -
