\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You didn't go visiting at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Well you'd to - my husband - my - well me husband didn't like going out to tea anywhere. He were very - he very - stand-offish, shy more - he were one of them, poor mixer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 And yet he took the children out a lot you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. Yes, but he were poor mixer, I mean, with other people. Poor mixer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yet you mixed with neighbours didn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, oh yes, me neighbours. I had good neighbours luv. I had - Tongue Fold, good neighbours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you take the children out shopping with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. Yes. Gertrude mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Your husband turned Roman Catholic for you, did he always go to church with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 He kept up the faith?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5177427\charrsid3816264 And he were very - he were took in the church St Osman\rquote 
s in Long Lane. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 The - do you know where that is - St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5177427\charrsid3816264 Osman's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
, Long Lane, well he was took in there and I - I'd requiem mass. Do you understand all that? Well he'd requiem mass and that's what they'll have to do with me, I want to go in St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5177427\charrsid3816264 Osman's}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 . Yes, well - me daughter and son. Was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
 there and - me youngest son, she were in Great Lever and they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  at St Peter and Paul. That were big change for us up there.
