\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5177427\charrsid3816264 Osman\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 , well we built our new church. We were proper good workers there. Anybody'll tell y
ou about Bob Longworth up Tongue Fold. I'm not frightened of telling my husband's name, one of the best. Yes.
