\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, we never talked about 'em. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Never discussed it in any way?
