\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh - well you see, I had a - a kit - a big kitche
n, my kitchen was a big kitchen, I had a little scullery outside and - we kept front for a sitting room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever have meals in the front if anybody came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well - not - not very often. But we have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Where did you cook then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Cooked in the kitchen, 'cos we'd a cook stove in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you mean gas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 A - gas. A gas cooker then you see, then. Oh yes, we'd cookers then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You say you never left the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 I did not. My }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 boy\rquote d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  tell you if he were here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you remember ever punishing your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Oh did I, aye, they got punished if they done some - oh yes. I've a boy sixty-two he came to see me last Thursday. I'm going - I'm going this Sunday to their house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you remember any special occasion when you punished them and how you felt about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, I don't think so, luv. No, they never did nothing really wrong. You know. To have a big punishing. No. Not to have a good punishing.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever have any musical instruments in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Well - yes. Well we didn't but child - - me son, where I'm going this Sunday, he - he wasn't musical but he wanted one, and I brought him this thing, those harmonica things you know. Yes, from Booth's, you know, proper musical place and - but he couldn't
 - he couldn't play it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever make music as a family, did anyone sing and make music as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, no, not really. We used to sing songs and that you know. We used to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 As a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, in the family way. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 In your family did you have books and magazines and newspapers in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. No. Oh yes, we had morning papers. And night - Evening News and - Daily }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 Dispatch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 . My husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 But you didn't belong to a library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you read aloud to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You went to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 Morecombe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  for your holidays didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, always went to Mor -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, every year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 How long did you go for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well, you know, for the week, we had a week then you know, weren't a fortnight then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 And you always went to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 Morecombe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When the children were growing up I know they went to Mass.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 They did and all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did they have different clothes, did they have special clothes for Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh they had Sunday clothes luv. Oh they never had 'em on through week, their Sunday clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What about you when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 , did you have Sunday clothes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. Yes. Yes, we used to - we used to have Sunday clothes. Oh yes. But - we always pulled them off, we didn't wear them in the house.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you or your husband ever go out to clubs or institutes or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. Oh he'd gone and had a drink. Oh not - not - not to clubs luv. Just - to a drink. Well not very often, well we couldn't afford
. Oh not when we'd children, oh no. Seventeen, that's why we never left them, no, and I never had no - nothing in the house, unless it were a drop of whisky or brandy. For if we weren't so well. That's all we had in the house. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever have any paid help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did relatives help you if you were ill or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well - well there were no relatives to help. All mine lived at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 Farnworth}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 , relatives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You told me you were never ill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. I've had a good health luv. I've always had -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
 did you have a lot of friends come visiting you, did you have a lot of friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, I have a lot of friends yet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When your children were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, I've friends who come and see me ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 They used to come and see you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You never used to go to see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, not so often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You invited them to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, well they'd come when they'd not been - they'd not stop so long you long know. Happen ha
ve a couple of hours and have a cup of tea and that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did they have to be invited?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
No, no, they could come just as they wanted. When they saw - out you know. We weren't like that you know, never having - everybody coming all at once like that. You know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Your home was rented when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5639861 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264  wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh - oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you remember - hour landlord and if you ever saw him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh I saw him every week when we paid the rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When your father got home from work in the evenings how many evenings would he stay in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh I don't think me dad went out so much then. He didn't go out so much luv. Me dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. He used to go o
ut at Saturday. He used to take me gran out for a drink at Friday. He used to go on his own at Saturday. Having a drink in the pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What did you call the other people who were not working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You belonged to the working class people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What did you call the other people who were not working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Oh we used to always say they're - they're well-off. They were well - well off. The well-off people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Why did you think they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 well off\\/}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well they thought they were when they weren't working. We had to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Who did you think were the well off people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well, we were - we were best well off when - when we - reckoned us up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Why - because we used to mix - we'd mix up with our own sort, we didn't want - well, they never bothered to look at you them as had }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 owt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
 did they. Oh no. I don't know. They always - they dressed nicer than you. You felt kind of - snubbed, you know, that way. Oh you never went out with 'em. Not in your own class. Well we didn't anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you think your granny saw herself as belonging to a certain class of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do what? No, she were only like us. She were brought up like us, me grandma.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You thought you were working class you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, we were working class, just working class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 When you were a child your home was rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, our home was rented.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you ever see that landlord at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well I - I don't know whether we did. When me grandma used to pay - it might have
 been when we were at school. But you see our landlord used to come very - every Friday night or Saturday afternoon, when I paid rent. Yes, I always paid rent. It were - it were five and three and - and it's not been built long, and when it, they charge y
ou - and it were - just got to a pound.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Were there any gangs or groups in your school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Gangs? I don't know, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you remember any children being left out of things?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Not at our school. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 St. Joseph's at Hallowell. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 And St Mary's at Bolton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You don't remember any gangs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. No gangs, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Do you think you benefited from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well I don't know. I may have, I was always a good scholar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You didn't have any part time jobs to earn any money did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You started part time first of all didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, I didn't work. Not when I was small, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 How did you get the job in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 How did I get - well - it was Musgroves on - 
Musgroves Mill on Chorley Old Road, because we lived on Chorley Old - just off Chorley Old Road, Avenue Street. No, we got there because they were wanting 'em at time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you see a notice or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No. No, no, no, notice and - me dad worked
 there for 'em and all you know. It was a good while before he got any wages. I worked there a twelve month. Me - me and me other sister, when she started she would stay and - she went to learning to - what they call a setter on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you say your brother got your father's wheel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 What did you mean by that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
Well when me dad died - he got me dad's wheel. Well - spinner, he got the wheels. Yes, what he had the cups made, cups with. His machine. They would call them machines. Th
ey were like - they're long big - great - big long things and they make cups for weavers, well then comes out and other goes in. You see, when they get so far it - and it goes back and the others coming out, and you have to keep going from one to another 
piecing their ends up. Right. Same as we say - how - how
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well Same as a weaver having looms, you'd say - well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You started part time in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes. I worked half time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 How did you feel about going to school when you were doing half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well - all right, I was all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did it change your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Well not as I know of, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Did you still want to go to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Yes, I were all right. I were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 You didn't mind going as well as going to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 No, not at all. Well it were only for twelve month you know. I went full time when I were fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7209395\charrsid3816264 Have you always been a jack tenter}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 I've always worked in the mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5246476 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 Except when you were in munitions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2833882 LL  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 That's right, went to munitions was on. That's all.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid16455581\charrsid3816264 
\par }}